name: taxi in kyoto
description:
a camera had always been a tool to capture memories for me, but this photo i took in kyoto made me realize it can be so much more. the world is full of colors, and as someone with aphantasia, this is one way I can cherish them forever. i've been learning through mistakes ever since, and it all started from here.

it only seems fitting that this photo would also be my first entry into the NFT space.
